metadata.name: For The First 10 Genesis Collectors of X-SURE Nixie Clock
metadata.description: X-SURE Nixie Clock may be the first intelligent nixie clock that can access the Internet and display dynamic data such as asset prices. Its rare "window" design and the ingenious combination of metal, glass and wood can protect the precious memory of mankind. These NFTs are for the first 10 genesis collectors of X-SURE Nixie Clock around the world.
